title: Episode 326 w/ NE-YO
itunes:title: Episode 326 w/ NE-YO
description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode we chop it up with the one and only NE-YO! 

The R&B legend joins us for an episode you don’t want to miss. Listen as NE-YO shares his journey, and talks about his come up as an artist and a songwriter.

NE-YO shares stories about working with Beyoncé, Michael Jackson and many more! 

Grab on to your fedora and strap in for the ride as NE-YO takes us through an episode that you don’t want to miss! 

Make some noise for NE-YO!!! 💐💐💐🏆🏆🏆

Listen and subscribe at http://www.drinkchamps.com
